media-libs/vapoursynth:vapoursynth_plugins_morpho - Enable simple morphological filters plugin
media-libs/vapoursynth:vapoursynth_plugins_ocr - Enable video frames Optical Character Recognition plugin using app-text/tesseract
media-libs/vapoursynth:vapoursynth_plugins_removegrain - Enable Remove Grain plugin
media-libs/vapoursynth:vapoursynth_plugins_subtext - Enable SSA/ASS subtitles plugin using media-libs/libass
media-libs/vapoursynth:vapoursynth_plugins_vinverse - Enable residual combing removal plugin
