media-libs/vapoursynth:vspipe - Enable support for piping output
media-libs/waifu2x-converter-cpp:cuda - Compiles with CUDA support.
media-libs/waifu2x-converter-cpp:models - Install models to use in the standalone app.
media-libs/waifu2x-converter-cpp:opencl - Compiles with OpenCL support.
media-video/mpv:archive - Enable support for various archive formats via app-arch/libarchive
media-video/mpv:bluray - Enable playback of Blu-ray filesystems
